sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get upgrade
sudo apt-get install gdebi-core
sudo apt-get install libwebkitgtk-3.0-0
wget http://steinerdatenbank.de/software/ghb_0.10.5-1_armhf.deb
sudo gdebi ghb_0.10.5-1_armhf.deb

the gui client is installed to /usr/bin under the name ghb
the cli is HandBrakeCLI
If there is a dependency missing, ghb will exit quietly